title: Elements of Metallurgy and Engineering Alloys by Campbell F (200
description:
Book Description:

The book combines a thorough presentation of physical and mechanical metallurgical concepts along with a practical survey of all important metals, their alloys, and their engineering properties. Easy to read and well illustrated, the book will be valuable to professionals and practitioners such as designers, structural engineers, material and process engineers, manufacturing engineers, materials engineers, and technicians.
